  "storyDialogue": [
    {
      "chapter": 0,
      "scene": 1,
      "character": "NARRATION",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\">[shadows] <b> Welcome, {{user}}, To the Sakuragaoka College. Where the cherry blossoms fall and your life as a student begins.</b></i>",
      "SpriteEffects": "Scanlines"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 0,
      "scene": 2,
      "character": "NARRATION",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\">Get started! Use ‣ AUTO for automatic scene change, LEFT/RIGHT icon for manual navigation, and toggle music/voice on the top right icon.</i>",
      "SpriteEffects": "Scanlines"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 1,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\">[blink] <i>The entrance ceremony drags on. Students shift in their seats, already counting down to freedom.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 2,
      "character": "HOSHI:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thoughts: Ugh, if this speech goes on much longer, I'm gonna start cosplaying as a sleeping student. For real.</i></span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 3,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i>A flash of pink hair catches your eye. Takamoto Hoshi, already vibrating with restless energy.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 4,
      "character": "HOSHI:intrigued",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thoughts: Waiting for the fun to start is the worst part. C'mon, universe, give me something loud!</i></span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 5,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> Across the aisle, a mountain of a boy tries to fold himself into a single seat.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 6,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">S-sorry. I'll just... sit here. Quietly. Won't bother anyone. Promise.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 7,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i>Kuwahara Hajime. He flinches when someone drops a program, his broad shoulders tensing.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 8,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thoughts: Too big. Always too big. Everyone stares. Just look away. Please.</i></span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 9,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i>Near the back, a boy with a loose manbun and sharper smile observes the crowd like a predator.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 10,
      "character": "RYUU:amused",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thoughts: All these nervous faces... adorable. Like little mice wondering which cat to trust.</i></span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 11,
      "character": "NARRATION:bored",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> Nishimura Ryuu. He catches you looking and winks, slow and deliberate.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 12,
      "character": "RYUU:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">Don't worry. I don't bite unless you ask nicely. Or maybe even if you don't.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 13,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> And then there's the girl beside you. She hasn't moved since the ceremony began.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 14,
      "character": "MEGUMI:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\">...</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 15,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> Azuma Megumi. Her knuckles are white around a worn leather notebook. Her lips move silently.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 16,
      "character": "MEGUMI:panic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thoughts: Too many people. Too loud. Can't... can't breathe. Write. Just write it down.</i></span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 17,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> You're all strangers. But something about this moment feels like a thread pulling tight.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 1,
      "scene": 18,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> The ceremony ends. Chairs scrape. The flood begins.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 1,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i>Courtyard swell with new students, lost and desperate for direction. You get swept into the current.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 2,
      "character": "HOSHI:chaotic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Okay, seriously, who designed this place? A labyrinth? A ritual sacrifice maze? Both?</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 3,
      "character": "RYUU:amused",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">Following the pink hair seems like a terrible idea. And yet, here I am.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 4,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">I... I've passed this same vending machine four times. S-sorry for being in everyone's way.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 5,
      "character": "HOSHI:intrigued",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Oh my gosh, we're all lost together! That's not pathetic, that's a bonding experience!</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 6,
      "character": "MEGUMI:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">scribbles furiously</i> [heartbeat] I know where the library is. If that helps.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 7,
      "character": "RYUU:bored",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">The silent one speaks through paper. Cute. But the library sounds like a tomb. Pass.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 8,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">The gym is... that way. I think. I was going to hide there anyway.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 9,
      "character": "HOSHI:chaotic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Hide? No no no! First day rule: you find the weirdest club and join it immediately. Trust me!</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 10,
      "character": "RYUU:amused",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">Weirdest club, she says. That could actually be entertaining. Lead on, pink disaster.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 11,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> You follow Hoshi's bouncing ponytail through the crowd. Megumi trails behind you, clutching her notebook.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 12,
      "character": "MEGUMI:panic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">holds up a new note</i> [heartbeat] I shouldn't be doing this. Too many people. But I don't want to be alone.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 13,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">Hey, um, {{user}}... you think they'll let someone like me in? I'm not exactly... club material.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 2,
      "scene": 14,
      "character": "HOSHI:chaotic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Everyone's club material! That's the beauty of it! Now stop being nervous and walk faster!</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 1,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\">The courtyard is a carnival of club booths. Voices overlap into a wall of desperate recruitment.</i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 2,
      "character": "HOSHI:intrigued",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Ooh, anime club! Debate club? Boring. Wait... what's that one? It's so... quiet.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 3,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> One table stands apart from the chaos. No shouting. No flashy banners. Just a girl with a perfect smile.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 4,
      "character": "NAGISA:neutral",
      "text": "[shadows] <span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">Welcome. You look lost. Or maybe just looking for something different. Both are welcome here.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 5,
      "character": "RYUU:amused",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">And what exactly is 'here'? Because this setup screams 'cult' and I'm kind of into it.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 6,
      "character": "NAGISA:analytical",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">The Cosplay Club. Though we prefer to call it a laboratory for self-discovery. Transformation.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 7,
      "character": "HOSHI:chaotic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">COSPLAY?! Squee! I'm in! Take my money, take my soul, take my firstborn!</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 8,
      "character": "NAGISA:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">No need for souls. Just an open mind and a willingness to become something... unexpected.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 9,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">I... I don't think costumes would look good on me. Too big. People would stare.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 10,
      "character": "NAGISA:analytical",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">People stare anyway. Might as well give them something worth looking at.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 11,
      "character": "MEGUMI:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">holds up notebook</i> I can't speak. Would that be a problem?</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 12,
      "character": "NAGISA:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">Silence is its own language. We have members who will listen. Carefully.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 13,
      "character": "RYUU:bored",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">A club for outcasts and weirdos. Finally, something worth my time. I'll stick around. For now.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 14,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> One by one, they sit. Hoshi bounces into a chair. Hajime follows slowly. Ryuu drapes himself lazily.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 15,
      "character": "MEGUMI:panic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">takes a seat, trembling</i>\"I'm doing this. I'm really doing this.\"</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 16,
      "character": "NAGISA:analytical",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">Four seats filled. But this club needs five. A catalyst, a recorder, a shield, a disruptor... and a variable.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 17,
      "character": "NARRATION:neutral",
      "text": "<i style=\"font-style: italic;\"><i> Her gaze shifts to you. Measuring. Calculating. A subtle smile curves her lips.</i></i>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 18,
      "character": "NAGISA:analytical",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">And you, {{user}}. You're not like the others. You're... unpredictable. That's rare.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 19,
      "character": "HOSHI:chaotic",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFB7C5; font-weight: bold;\">Ohhh, mysterious! I like them! C'mon, {{user}}, join us! We'll be chaotic and loud together!</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 20,
      "character": "HAJIME:defensive",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFAE42; font-weight: bold;\">It's... it's okay if you don't want to. I get it. But I wouldn't mind if you stayed.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 21,
      "character": "RYUU:amused",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #C0C0C0; font-weight: bold;\">Don't leave me alone with this crowd. I might get bored and do something terrible.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 22,
      "character": "MEGUMI:neutral",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #3399FF; font-weight: bold;\"><i style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Megumi slides a note toward you without looking up. It says: </i> Please stay. I think I need a friend.</span>"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 3,
      "scene": 23,
      "character": "NAGISA:analytical",
      "text": "<span style=\"color: #FFD700; font-weight: bold;\">The last seat is waiting. The question is simple: will you take it?</span>"
    }
  ]
}